display_long_description:
Cube Jumper VR

Step into the immersive, cube-filled world of Cube Jumper VR, where one wrong step could send you plunging into lethal lava! Designed for VR, this fast-paced platformer challenges your reflexes and agility as you jump, collect pickups, and survive increasingly difficult levels—all in a stunning, 3D virtual reality environment. Collecting diamonds and shooting targets not only helps you progress to the next level but also earns you valuable points. These points contribute to your ranking on the global leaderboard, adding a competitive edge to your gameplay.

Game Modes:

    • Free Play: Explore the cube world at your own pace, collect pickups, and master your jumping skills.

    • Time Attack: Race against the clock for the fastest time while navigating tricky levels and avoiding dangerous falls.

    • Shooter: Grab your weapon and take on hostile NPCs like spiders and drones. Shoot down targets while keeping yourself above the lava.

Key Features:

    • Immersive VR Gameplay: Experience platforming like never before in full 3D, where every jump and fall feels real.

    • Pickups and Power-ups: Collect diamonds and resources to enhance your abilities and score higher.

    • Three Game Modes: Free Play for exploration, Time Attack for speedrunners, and Shooter for those who love action-packed combat.

    • Intense Combat: In Shooter mode, defend yourself against a variety of enemies, avoid traps, and shoot at targets to complete levels.

Get ready to jump into action!
